Job Description
Responsibilities:Work on PeopleSoft or Human resources projects involving strategy, production support, implementation support and performance optimization related to information technology operations, business processes, security and data integrity for the PeopleSoft applicationsAbility to manage multiple projects, multiple teams at the same time catering to 12 geographical locations.Participate in PeopleSoft business processes mapping and in the day-to-day activities of ERP advisory engagements including process analysis and design, gap analysis, functional system design and specifications, system configuration, development of system tests, procedures, and documentationIdentify and communicate findings/presentations to senior management.Vendor management and managing key stakeholders in HRMG
