Company profile:
Established in 2003, HEAD HUNTERS HR Pvt. Ltd. pioneered the concept of Turnkey Hiring Projects in India. With a vast experience and in-depth understanding of precise requirements in the recruitment process, we provide immeasurable value to both employers and jobseekers.
In this dynamic environment and competitive market place, our rigorous search methodologies and extensive database help us provide your organization with the right human resources including permanent as well as flexi-staffing solutions to maintain that competitive edge. Our timely and goal-oriented services across several domains offer several benefits in terms of time, cost and administration.
Dedication involves making the space to let young ideas take hold. Every tree was once a seed and every company was once, an idea. At HEAD HUNTERS, that is exactly what we do.
In order to keep updated with the latest, our human resource experts attend regular upgrading training sessions. By maintaining confidentiality of information gathered during this process, we make sustained relations with our clients possible in the long run.
